author: Danny Schwartz
title: Mike-WiLL Made It Reveals "Ransom 2" Tracklist
text:
Home > News > Mike-WiLL Made It Reveals "Ransom 2" Tracklist Mike-WiLL Made It Reveals "Ransom 2" Tracklist 6 1 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Feb 22, 2017 at 04:22pm Mike WiLL Made-It appears to be angling for a March release of "Ransom 2." 
Mike WiLL Made-It has shared some essential information regarding his long-anticipated mixtape Ransom 2 in the past 24 hours. He posted a Twitter video featuring the Ransom 2 tracklist on his iTunes. None of three songs he has previously indicated would be on the project ( "By Chance" feat. Rae Sremmurd, "Al Sharpton" feat. Future, or "Nothing is Promised" feat Rihanna ) are present. "Making tweaks n shit once I turn in final record I will drop release date," Mike explained in the Twitter caption. 
He also informed fans that he would share the "REAL release date shortly" and indicated that March will likely be the month when Ransom 2 finally arrives.
